item.title: SpawnPoiint Inspired My Display
item.description: I’ve shared his videos in another post and when I moved into my home1 his place was a major inspiration to the aesthetic I was after there. A lot of stuff he recommended I purchased and my favorite, besides the GeekMadeDesigns stuff2 is his shelf full of gaming consoles and accessories. I couldn’t find his exact shelf as he is in the UK, but I found one similar at Wayfair and purchased it.
